description:
Made of durable zirconia ceramic, the Oura Ring 4 comes in four additional colors, designed naturally with minerals: tide (soft blue), cloud (ivory), petal (light pink) and midnight (dark blue). title: Unboxing the $499 Ceramic Oura Ring 4 in Tide 💍

author: CNET
description: The BOYA Magic is a versatile wireless microphone that can used in four different forms: handheld, clip-on, on-camera, and desktop. It comes with two transmitters and a receiver that is all attached to the charging case that can be used as a handheld mic so it’s very company. The mini mics weigh 7 grams and individually have 6hrs of battery life featuring AI noise cancellation with the ability to block out up to 40dB of noise. The BOYA Magic combo we have here is $130 for all the bells and whistles but there is more affordable packs as well. #boya #boyamagic #tech #contentcreator #wirelessmicrophone #mobilemic #noisecancellation
title: Unboxing the BOYA Magic, An AI-Powered Transformable Wireless Microphone
